{"tid":822473,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹襲港】科大宣布明天學生及教職員均無須回校","createTime":"2018-09-16T10:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T13:00:59.000Z","uid":20058,"like":57,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0d4a2c0dce1ea8baf112847508c2102daf3acda3","tid":822473,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"香港科技大學宣佈，由於強颱風山竹襲港，於全港各區造成破壞，考慮到多個交通管道受到影響，大學方面亦有設施需要清理及維修，為確保學生及員工的安全，大學決定明日無論是否仍有熱帶氣旋警告或暴雨警告訊號發出，科大學生及教職員均無須回校。​​<br />\n<br />\n【山竹襲港】科大宣布明天學生及教職員均無須回校<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/?refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2F%3Frefer%3DShare&d=v5teIVfqnhJLvNGsZBJNkbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=d033cde4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2F%3Frefer%3DShare&h=1b16d13d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/?refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"9e1acc2bf61cfeab082cd9c3ee8d952b8875d5da","tid":822473,"uid":37719,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:55:15.000Z","msg":"科大=一大"},{"pid":"eecbe7fa931f6328b92b23db596e04ee6a25caa9","tid":822473,"uid":123499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9666afbbeb2df630a771f2e7dcf261f6049556b1","tid":822473,"uid":205143,"like":8,"dislike":18,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:56:31.000Z","msg":"假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a586fdd7b5a900384d87a89c130f094db2a77a3","tid":822473,"uid":124156,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:57:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 